cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict the popularity of hashtag compounds on Twitter. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves data mining and information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper uses statistical models and machine learning algorithms, which could be categorized under cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
